summary: CHECK ENGINE LIGHT KEEPS COMING BACK ON AFTER REPAIR.  HAS BEEN REPAIRED 3 TIMES OVER THE PAST FEW MONTHS AND IT CAME BACK ON AGAIN 2 DAYS AFTER IT HAD BEEN REPAIRED THE LAST TIME.
